## EXCHANGE: BINANCE THAILAND
- Base URL: https://api.binance.th
- Auth: X-MBX-APIKEY header + timestamp/signature in query params
- Signature: HMAC-SHA256 of full query string
- Timestamp: milliseconds int(time.time() * 1000)
- Symbol format: BTCUSDT (NOT THB_BTC)
- Klines: GET /api/v1/klines — response timestamp in MS divide by 1000
- Fee: 0.1% per side = 0.2% round trip

## TRADING MODES
scalping:     EMA(9/21) + RSI(7) + Hull MA + Volume | SL 1.0% TP 3.0% | ATR×1.2
trend_only:   EMA(50/200) + MACD + ADX + Fisher + TEMA | SL 4.5% TP 10.0% | ATR×1.8
standard:     all strategies | SL 2.0% TP 4.0% | ATR×1.5

## KEY CLASSES
- SignalGenerator: aggregates 7 strategies, runs risk checks
- RiskManager: Kelly sizing, daily loss limit, drawdown guard
- BinanceThClient: all API calls (renamed from BitkubClient)
- BinanceThCollector: OHLCV + historical backfill
- TelegramCommandHandler: /status /stop /pause /mode commands
- PreTradeGate: 10-point checklist before every order
- MinimalROI: Freqtrade-inspired time-based profit table
- WeeklyReviewer: Sunday auto-review + grade A-F

## CODING RULES
- async/await throughout — never time.sleep() in async
- Type hints on ALL functions
- Never use print() — use logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)
- All config from bot_config.yaml — never hardcode numbers
- Klines timestamp: row[0] is MS → int(row[0] / 1000) for seconds
- Candle buffer: deque(maxlen=500) per symbol/interval
- All API calls: try/except + 3 retries + exponential backoff
- Never crash main loop — catch Exception and continue

